---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
---

<MainLayout title="Go Rank First IA">
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-primary-dark text-white py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4 md:mb-6">
Go Rank First <span class="text-white/90">Inteligencia Artificial</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8 opacity-90">
Revoluciona tu estrategia de posicionamiento con soluciones de IA de vanguardia. Optimiza tu presencia online y alcanza los primeros resultados de búsqueda.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center space-y-4 sm:space-y-0 sm:space-x-4">
        <a 
          href="/contacto" 
          class="bg-white text-primary px-6 md:px-8 py-3 md:py-4 rounded-windsurf hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors font-semibold text-sm md:text-base">
          Solicitar Consulta
        </a>
        <a 
          href="#servicios" 
          class="border-2 border-white text-white px-6 md:px-8 py-3 md:py-4 rounded-windsurf hover:bg-white hover:text-primary transition-colors font-semibold text-sm md:text-base">
          Conocer Más
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="servicios" class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16 md:py-24">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-12 md:mb-16 text-text-primary">
Servicios de <span class="text-primary">Go Rank First IA</span>
    </h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="bg-surface/80 rounded-3xl shadow-md transition-all duration-300 p-8 hover:bg-accent/5 hover:scale-102 hover:shadow-lg cursor-pointer">
        <Icon name="mdi:chart-line" class="w-12 h-12 text-accent mb-4 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:scale-105 group-hover:brightness-110" />
        <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-wide mb-4 text-accent transition-colors duration-300">Optimización SEO con IA</h3>
        <p class="text-text-secondary">
          Análisis avanzado y estrategias de posicionamiento impulsadas por inteligencia artificial.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-surface/80 rounded-3xl shadow-md transition-all duration-300 p-8 hover:bg-accent/5 hover:scale-102 hover:shadow-lg cursor-pointer">
        <Icon name="mdi:content-copy" class="w-12 h-12 text-accent mb-4 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:scale-105 group-hover:brightness-110" />
        <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-wide mb-4 text-accent transition-colors duration-300">Generación de Contenido</h3>
        <p class="text-text-secondary">
          Contenido optimizado y personalizado generado con tecnología de IA de última generación.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-surface/80 rounded-3xl shadow-md transition-all duration-300 p-8 hover:bg-accent/5 hover:scale-102 hover:shadow-lg cursor-pointer">
        <Icon name="mdi:analytics" class="w-12 h-12 text-accent mb-4 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:scale-105 group-hover:brightness-110" />
        <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-wide mb-4 text-accent transition-colors duration-300">Análisis de Rendimiento</h3>
        <p class="text-text-secondary">
          Monitoreo y análisis predictivo del rendimiento de tu estrategia digital.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>
